thread.title: Number 2 House Republican: votes not there for 'clean' debt limit bill
thread.title_full: Number 2 House Republican: votes not there for 'clean' debt limit bill | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Number 2 House Republican: votes not there for 'clean' debt limit bill
text:
WASHINGTON U.S. House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy said on Tuesday a "clean" bill to raise the U.S. debt limit that did not include sweeteners for Republicans would not win a majority in the House of Representatives.
"I do not see 218 for any clean bill," McCarthy told reporters.
(Reporting by Richard Cowan ; Writing by Tim Ahmann ; Editing by Sandra Maler )
